用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"4f0f047cae2de34d65695c8ddce1fd4a50ab043b","tid":1776289,"uid":245286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"到最後以為會有台灣場，點知係冇......噉可唔可以開香港encore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10b895e8a2b230d7dc9f9847db7212bc1d6cbcf","tid":1776289,"uid":158067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"睇左兩年佢既演唱會。<br />\n不過佢真係冇乜新歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。雖然舊歌都夠做。<br />\n同埋佢啲歌大部份都係慘情歌，但係又選擇係新年開，好難攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係咪黃我就唔知，不過佢好重視小朋友將來既教育，所以佢鑊鑊都係diu教育局。 希望佢唔好跪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421bc167c8e366f1621f04062afb5cb0b7bc420b","tid":1776289,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7280a67db1137b3ca7e5a5643ea810f5a155e73","tid":1776289,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"33fc4cfc8bfc969a71d51a6d9dba78a9a31af077","tid":1776289,"uid":10903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:49:31.000Z","msg":"支持鄭中基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw兩次香港站出碟未？<br />\n<br />\n支持佢再開多次香港站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"支持 <br />\n唔洗搞咁多花臣唱歌跳舞, 淨唱兩個鐘都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T06